      "updated": 1778016101
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa5f6700000000007dfab8",
      "text": " 1. [Evergreen notes should be atomic]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778016104,
      "updated": 1778016120
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa5f7800000000007dfab9",
      "text": " 2. [Evergreen notes should be concept-oriented]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778016120,
      "updated": 1778016120
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa5f7800000000007dfaba",
      "text": " 3. [Evergreen notes should be densely linked]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778016120,
      "updated": 1778016120
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa5f7800000000007dfabb",
      "text": " 4. [Prefer associative ontologies to hierarchical taxonomies]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778016120,
      "updated": 1778016120
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa5f7800000000007dfabc",
      "text": " 5. [Write notes for yourself by default, disregarding audience]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778016120,
      "updated": 1778016120
    },
    {
